      <title>铜价延续跌势，创纪录价格令中国买家望而却步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/copper-extends-decline-as-record-prices-deter-buyers-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国工厂不愿支付创纪录的价格，铜价连续第三天下跌。美联储官员的鹰派言论也给基本金属带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/copper-extends-decline-as-record-prices-deter-buyers-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
